item.description:
This month, Rajesh Jaiswal will be presenting his entrpreneurial ideas and goals. He will provide us with a background of his current situation and involvement in his different companies.
The other members of the group will provide him with feedback and recommendations to help him advance to the next level of success.
The meeting is confidential and all disclosures therein are meant solely for the use of the participants and should not be shared outside of the group without the express consent and permission of the presenter.
All participants agree to maintain the strict confidentiality of any proprietary information that may be disclosed by members to the group.
Thank you very much.
